<h2 id="automation-sort-objects">Automation: Sort Objects</h2>
<p>Sorts cards/pieces in the specified holders.</p>
<p>Objects will be sorted to the same order they&#39;re listed in the card deck widget, which can be changed by editing the deck and dragging entries in the Cards tab.</p>
<h3 id="holders">Holders</h3>
<p>Click the button to enter selection mode, from selection mode click on holders or Player Seats to choose where to sort cards/pieces.</p>
<h3 id="direction">Direction</h3>
<p>Sort ascending or descending.</p>
